Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Captain Tsukioka from the Satellite Patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have found a wrecked rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The site is P-75. All assemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They are space gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tsukioka! Space gangs have escaped to W-38.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Block them! -Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Stop pursuing them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They are headed to the space airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... They hid there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Space Airport R-45
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A space shuttle from Earth have arrived at the space airport R-45.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where rockets that travel to Moon or further gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockets from all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The space airport is a resting place for rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very crowded and busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Space airports looks like a downtown of a big city inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,People and robots come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There are hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Movies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And restaurants!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are dishes that are not available at the end of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocket workers can finally have their Earth food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right now on my way to meet the space airport director
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to discuss recent space gang problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a souvenir store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. We have everything. We are the best for space souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Meteor piece for kimchi jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Mars postcards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Back issues of magazine from Earth. $1 for a bundle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a frozen monster from Venus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. Can I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You need a new spacesuit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new seamless spacesuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's $320 for both top and bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir. I wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? We also have some guide books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel guide books, traveling rocket guide books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 20 cents a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, about that space gang...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Space gang? Ah, well that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't sell them here. Ask somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! I don't want to be involved with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we are good citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to fight against violence with justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! If you are a good citizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's better for you to just ignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay? -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, it's your responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been managing this space airport for 30 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time for you to retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep making mistakes, people will lose confidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocket accidents happen everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, the number of guests in my hotel has decreased a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this will be over like this? You have to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get a new airport director.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I still have some work left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you take your word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, no more rocket accidents, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a greedy old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time for him to step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be the new director.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the eleventh one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now my dad's credibility will get lower and lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr.Tsukioka? -That's right. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Atom, a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is robot doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help get rid of space gangs upon Dr.Ochanomizu's order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but it's not something a robot can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello! What? Space gangs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The site is about 160,000Km to Bethelkius Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Space gangs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't come to place like this. It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But please let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gangs did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! It's an evidence. It will be a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can figure out, because I'm a robot as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot saw the face of the criminal. For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird. Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's carrying something. It looks like a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He threw a corpse away in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tsukio, you are home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I've been hearing rumors. Is there a pressure for you to retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will arrest gangs for sure, so please don't retire. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't. I'm going to work more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. You used to be that small 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born in this Satellite R-45 and grew up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,R-45 and you are more precious than my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'd give that up? It's better for me to die than to leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to finish my life here on R-45.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be discouraged by some attacks or blames.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so downhearted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep. It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. We have everything. We are the best for space souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A sample of wrecked rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairy's costume piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the famous Venus cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop once you take a bite. How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Two more bites, you will fall in love. -You are so cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more bites! Would you like to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty box of Venus cake on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. You are from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many customers in your store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Those who buy and sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do. I'm not going to buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot was destroyed inside a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot's brain stop working as soon as it's destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so the last afterimage should be recorded in its electronic brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see someone recorded in its electronic brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, have you ever seen this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that man who came to sell that jewel yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does he live? He came to sell jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say something stupid, we will get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A good citizen shouldn't be involved in such!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! I want to tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, if you want to talk about it so bad, then go talk inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you talk inside here, no one outside will be able to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Go ahead. -I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... so he was trying to sell jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's staying in hotel? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, sir. I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You heard everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I heard what you said inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My ears can amplify up to 1,000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be easy on me. Pretend you didn't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The 120,000-ton cargo ship Arzanon was attacked again by space gangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Precious metals that were to be sent to Earth were all stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Space gangs are beyond control lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Airport director Tsukioka is being held responsible for such incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to keep your position after all these mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking on behalf of all people in the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please consider it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One more attack, and that old man will be retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't call me boss in a place like this! -I'm sorry,Bo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't surprise me! You picked it up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked it up floating in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an empty case of a robot again. It's very elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This face looks exactly like Captain Tsukioka, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't understand. What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already picked up the same thing five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them have the same face. Besides, they are getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, hide in the airport director's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And figure his secret out! There should be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the job. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would notice that I'm a gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's odd. Nothing's happening since he entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let me amplify the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This sound is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's the sound of deflating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it was useful to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The director takes that robot down and goes somewhere to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, that's... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a robot that looks exactly like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukio, I'm sorry I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'd have to tell you everything. Please don't be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you are not human. You are a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukio, listen to me. I didn't have a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a robot child and raised it, considering it as my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you know about the story of Dr.Tenma and Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When Dr.Tenma made Atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom didn't grow even after time had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So Dr.Tenma was disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to raise you like a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I changed your body every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Into a bigger one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been throwing old bodies away like this secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. I didn't tell you because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I be a captain of men when I'm just a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My, not even a drop of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Tsukio! I caught the space gang boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The space gang boss is the president of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, let's go arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are late, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a robot. A robot cannot arrest a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they find out that I'm a robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fooled everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Tsukio, don't be too sad about such fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been through this as well. But I cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should cheer up as well, Mr.Tsukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are under arrest, Rossham.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I under arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are behind the space gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are falsely accusing. I won't forgive you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an evidence. There is a witness as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I also heard an interesting story. I also have an evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you are a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Walls have ears. I heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a robot. Just a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell your secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If people find out about your secret, they will all abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Airport director will be fired as well, since he fooled everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead! Arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids! Get this arrogant robot's fingers burnt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare a robot try to arrest a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Why wouldn't you arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a robot can fight against villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Get up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed him, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Double door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Tsukio, dispatch the patrol! I'll follow them as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Patrol team is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'll be done with such bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss of the space gang that have been intimidating us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was surprisingly the hotel president, Rossham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to resolve this case thanks to Captain Tsukioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give him an applause for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, they all welcomed me even after they had found out that I'm a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Tsukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best. This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing well, Mr.Tsukio. I'm going back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Space airport looks crowded and busy today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And both the airport director and captain will carry their duties out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorial is the biggest spaceship in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win the first place with the essay about your dream, you can get a chance to ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But robots... cannot dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I sealed my super power for 24 hours to be like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that moment, the spaceship was hijacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? My seven powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Spaceship in Imminent Danger"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:24:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
